Decent price for a good dvd, my grandson enjoys watching power rangers. The movie came a day earlier than expected.

You can't go wrong with any of the Power Ranger series of DVDs. I've purchased them for my nephew and he loves every one of them. The content is clean and many of them have moral themes. Some might say it's violent but compared to some of the cartoons and other kid shows out there, the Power Rangers are mild. Good for all kids. Price could be lower.

Every Power Rangers series brought its own style to the show that made it a great series.  Ninja Storm brought its own style and this DVD shows that the best use of scenery and special effects to date.
